WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.000
In other words, several people have been injured as two trains collided on the London route.

2
00:00:04.000 --> 00:00:09.000
A train collision has taken place from the north of London, which has left at least one person dead.

3
00:00:09.000 --> 00:00:12.000
Emergency crews have been rushed to bed for shire.

4
00:00:12.000 --> 00:00:18.000
The train crash site witness describes the scene as a bomb explosion-like impact after the crash.

